## CRUD Testing

The complete CRUD flow was tested using Swagger UI:

1. Create a task using `POST /tasks`
2. Retrieve tasks using `GET /tasks`
3. Update a task using `PUT /tasks/{id}`
4. Delete a task using `DELETE /tasks/{id}`

All endpoints successfully respond with JSON data and proper HTTP status codes.
